{"type": "article", "id": 27629, "title": "香水包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-01T06:57:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702120257xeyH8mOF1I04v5li.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>这个名为 FACES 的香水包装设计是加拿大设计师 <a href=\"http://www.thibaultmagni.fr/index.html\">Thibault Magni</a> 的作品。FACES 的晶莹剔透的瓶身就好像是电影《了不起的盖茨比》中华丽的吊灯坠饰，在金色的映衬下显得格外奢华。香水的外盒则采用了反棱镜的形状，就像是为瓶子量身打造的镀金的茧。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120255OlnUDcQfMdxW48sp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120256bv68y39lfYcDz7Xe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120256jFbS9Ot7nKird6UT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702120257jy4Eql7imCI6KGsJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}